sentences: Black takes his stage name from Mars Blackman, a character that appeared in Air Jordan commercials directed by Spike Lee in the 1980s.
His debut album, Folks Music, was released on Team Love Records in 2004 to mixed reviews.
He toured with such acts as Bright Eyes and The Faint in 2005.
In 2008, he released his second full-length for Team Love, Stay Black.
